Coro::ProcessPool
=================

Provides a light-weight process pool.

    use Coro::ProcessPool;

    my $pool = Coro::ProcessPool->new(
        max_procs => 4,
        max_reqs  => 100,
    );

    my %result;
    foreach my $i (1 .. 1000) {
        $result{$i} = $pool->process(sub { shift * 2 }, $i);
    }

    $pool->shutdown;
